The benefits of image recognition in the education sector is for example to perhaps support disdavanatged kids to learn.
Good image recognition will help the kids notice the small details and difference between images helping them to learn things quicker and effective.
A limitation is helping the learning the subject of the image for example where the computer can explain the facts or details about the subject.
A risk is that people are becoming more and more reliable of this and sometimes computers may break down leaving no resource for learning.
